  "response": "Sadhguru, also known as Jaggi Vasudev, is an Indian yogi, mystic, and author who founded the Isha Foundation, a nonprofit organization that offers yoga programs and social outreach initiatives. Opinions about Sadhguru can vary widely. Some people admire him for his teachings on spirituality, well-being, and environmental issues, while others are skeptical and may consider him controversial or critical of some of his views and practices.\n\nWhether or not someone perceives him as a \"conman\" often depends on personal beliefs, experiences, and interpretations of his teachings. It's essential for individuals to do their own research, consider multiple perspectives, and come to an informed conclusion.",
